Name: Google Gmail - Read Email
Description: Read an email in user's Gmail account
Params: email: A description of the email to read - can include things like subject, sender, text from the contents of the email, etc.
Share Tools: github.com/gptscript-ai/tools/apis/google/gmail/read
Type: input

#!/bin/env bash

cat << EOF

Use the Google Gmail tools to find the email specified within these <input> tags: <input>${EMAIL}</input>.
If the <input>${EMAIL}</input> is empty, refer to your history to select the most relevant email to use.
Read the email and display the results.

EOF

